data.description: Stunning family home conveniently located near shopping centers, parks, and schools. The spacious interior features remodeled kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, bar area, large dining room, and a luxurious primary bedroom with vaulted ceiling. Walk-in closet. Fully fenced yard offers a safe space for outdoor activities and family fun. Property has been meticulously maintained, with a 30-year architectural roof installed in 2015 and a newer HVAC system with new ductwork installed in 2021. Energy efficiency has been enhanced with sealed attic and roofline. Move-in ready! Hurry, it won’t last.
